1.What is cloud Computing?
ANs: Cloud computing is nothing but on-demand delivery of IT-Resources over the internet.
you can access technical resources such as: comppute power, networking, security, databases etc
with pay-as-you-go pricing model.

Example: Cloud Providers into market (AWS, Azure, GCP_)

why cloud?
Instead of Buying servers, managing datacenters, handling cooling, power, network, security

you no need to worry about anything AWS provides everything as a service

